Name: Yancey-Lisa R.
Description:
Yancey-Lisa was stabbed once in the abdomen and four times in the back.

Yancey was a neighbour of [Barbarella](https://tdor.translivesmatter.info/reports/1975/03/15/barbarella_san-francisco-california-usa_2a097454), who had been killed three weeks earlier.

Source: Crusader, May 1975
